\u00f8kere fra flere ulike land.", "De involverte i knivdramaet onsdag bodde i samme oppgang, men mottaksledelsen er ikke kjent med at det har v\u00e6rt tidligere konflikt mellom partene.", "- Beboerne tar situasjonen rimelig greit, men noen er naturligvis bekymret. Vi m\u00e5 forsikre dem om at sikkerheten ved mottaket er god, sier Mathisen."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|moreromsdal"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "9fcc197486146328ed0b9127ec8569730a047f99ef2c37c86c3c3c2f3500e9dd"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-04-29T14:49:31.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Mannen bak knivdramaet ved Tingvoll asyls\u00f8kermottak f\u00e5r n\u00e5 psykiatrisk hjelp."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article13475366.ece/357o5k/ALTERNATES/w980-default/14393414_10153712083391277_1199511207_o.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/d49a4ae75a55dacdc785577d6ee1c08d974600de.jpg?59899b13"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Gjerningsmann f\u00e5r psykiatrisk behandling etter knivdrama -adressa.no", "Flere avh\u00f8rt", "Bekymrede beboere"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "d49a4ae75a55dacdc785577d6ee1c08d974600de"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["Tingvoll", "asylmottak", "asyls\u00f8kere", "Nordm\u00f8re"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Tingvoll,asylmottak,asyls\u00f8kere,Nordm\u00f8re"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "moreromsdal"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "law-government-and-politics"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["asyls\u00f8kere", "psykiatrisk", "knivdrama", "psykiatrisk behandling", "mottak"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["nordm\u00f8re", "adresseavisen"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "tingvoll"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": 